OL,3,CPrince of Wales cheers as Aston Villa
OL,4,Chead to Europa League final
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales was pictured
OL,7,Fpumping his fists in the air before
OL,8,Fcelebrating with Aston Villa's players
OL,9,Fin the dressing room after they
OL,10,Freached the Europa League final.
OL,12,FVilla fan William was photographed
OL,13,Fcheering from the stands during their
OL,14,F4-0 victory against Nottingham Forest,
OL,15,Fwhich secured a 4-1 aggregate win and
OL,16,Fset up a meeting with Freiburg in the
OL,17,Ffinal on May 20.
OL,19,FAston Villa manager Unai Emery
OL,20,Fconfirmed William had joined in with
OL,21,Fpost-match celebrations.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
