OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778256667
OL,3,CPrince of Wales cheers as Aston Villa
OL,4,Chead to Europa League final
OL,6,F"He was in the dressing room with the
OL,7,Fplayers and with me, and of course, he
OL,8,Fis so happy as well," the Spaniard
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FWilliam was joined by club ambassador
OL,12,FAhmed Elmohamady in the Villa Park
OL,13,Fstands in Birmingham.
OL,15,FChris Wood's penalty in the first leg
OL,16,Fhad given Vitor Pereira's Forest side
OL,17,Fthe edge but Ollie Watkins levelled
OL,18,Fthe aggregate scores in the 36th
OL,19,Fminute.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]
