OL,3,CPrince of Wales cheers as Aston Villa
OL,4,Chead to Europa League final
OL,6,FForest failed to deliver the type of
OL,7,Fperformance that saw them go 10 games
OL,8,Funbeaten and they went behind in the
OL,9,Ftie 13 minutes after the interval,
OL,10,Fcourtesy of Emi Buendia's penalty,
OL,11,Fbefore John McGinn's double sealed a 4-
OL,12,F1 aggregate win and a trip to Istanbul.
OL,14,FWilliam, patron of the Football
OL,15,FAssociation, is a passionate Villa
OL,16,Fsupporter and has followed the
OL,17,FMidlands club since he was a schoolboy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
