OL,3,CPrince of Wales cheers as Aston Villa
OL,4,Chead to Europa League final
OL,6,FHe was born less than a month after
OL,7,FVilla's most famous continental
OL,8,Fsuccess, when they beat Bayern Munich
OL,9,Fto lift the European Cup in May 1982.
OL,11,FIt is not yet known whether the prince
OL,12,Fwill travel to Istanbul for the final
OL,13,Flater this month.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
